target: You're very welcome, enjoy your Cambridge visit!
context: <user>  I need to book a train for Monday going to Cambridge please. <system>  There are quite a few trains that could suit your needs. Can you tell me where you would like to depart from? <user>  I'll be at London's Kings Cross and wanting to leave after 11:45 am. <system>  There is a train that leaves London Kings Cross at 13:17 and arrives in Cambridge at 14:08. Does that time work for you? <user>  Yes, that sounds fine. Can you book me tickets for 8 people, please? <system>  Your booking was successful. The total fee is 188.8 GBP payable at the station. The reference number is 2EGCVFWC <user>  Thank you goodbye <system>  Thank you and goodbye.<user>  Before you go, could you help me find an expensive restaurant in the city centre? <system>  Do you have a preference for the type of food?<user>  Yes, I'd like some classic British cuisine. <system>  Midsummer House Restaurant serves British food. Would you like me to book you a table?<user>  Yes, that place sounds perfect. If I could book for 8 on the same day at 15:00 it would be great. <system>  Booking was successful. The table will be reserved for 15 minutes. Reference number is : P0T1HLVC . Is there anything more I can do for you?<user>  That will be all. Thanks for your time. Bye. <system>
